response.original_title: 虹のコンキスタドール 真冬の野音2days「真夏の夢は単純じゃない！」DAY2
response.overview: An exclusive live broadcast of the final day of the two-day midwinter Nijicon live show held at Hibiya Park Concert Hall in Tokyo! Nakamura Akari, Tsurumi Moe, and Shimizu Riko will be graduating at this performance. It's sure to be an emotional stage for long-time fans as they recall the enthusiastic day they first met!
response.title: 虹のコンキスタドール 真冬の野音2days「真夏の夢は単純じゃない！」DAY2
